# Code Owners - Automated Review Assignments
#
# These owners will be automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull request
# that modifies files matching the patterns below.
#
# Learn more: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Database Schema - Requires Data Engineer approval
backend/prisma/schema.prisma @data-engineer
backend/prisma/migrations/ @data-engineer

# CI/CD Configuration - Requires Tech Lead approval
.github/workflows/ @tech-lead

# Documentation - Tech Lead reviews for technical accuracy
docs/ @tech-lead
*.md @tech-lead

# Agent Instructions - All agents should review changes to their own files
.claude/agents/tech-lead.md @tech-lead
.claude/agents/junior-engineer.md @junior-engineer
.claude/agents/data-engineer.md @data-engineer
.claude/agents/ux-designer.md @ux-designer

# Frontend Components - UX Designer reviews user-facing changes
frontend/src/components/ @ux-designer
frontend/src/pages/ @ux-designer

# API Routes - Tech Lead reviews for architecture
backend/src/routes/ @tech-lead

# Default - Tech Lead reviews everything not explicitly assigned
* @tech-lead
